      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "传说远古的梵天神殿里，立着三根金刚石柱子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-2",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/yunxi/recursion-rec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "想办法把上面的 n 减 1 个盘子，借助中间柱先挪到旁边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-3",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/yunxi/recursion-rec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.64,
      "size": 42192,
      "text": "再把最大的盘直接放到目标柱，最后把那 n 减 1 个盘搬过来盖上，这就是递归。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "steps",
      "line_id": "step-1",
      "filename": "steps-step-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/yunxi/steps-step-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.82,
      "size": 45072,
      "text": "设搬 n 个盘要 T 步，那么搬 n 加 1 个，就得先搬走 T 步、放大盘一步、再搬回 T 步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "steps",
      "line_id": "step-2",
      "filename": "steps-step-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/yunxi/steps-step-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "于是步数每次翻一倍还多一步，算下来正好是 2 的 n 次方减 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "steps",
      "line_id": "step-3",
      "filename": "steps-step-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/yunxi/steps-step-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "三个盘要七步，四个盘十五步，五个盘三十一步，一步都省不掉。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "doom",
      "line_id": "doom-1",
      "filename": "doom-doom-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/yunxi/doom-doom-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "传说僧侣搬完六十四个金盘之时，就是世界末日。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "doom",
